comments: Green (GSW) misses the jump shot attempt and the ball goes out of bounds.
DiVincenzo (GSW) moves laterally into Hardy's (DAL) path and initiates body contact that affects Hardy's SQBR during the drive.
Bullock (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Curry (GSW) on the perimeter.
Curry (GSW) places his off-arm against Bullock (DAL) with no extension and the contact is marginal.
Green (GSW) is established in Bullock's (DAL) path and he absorbs the contact to his upper body.
Wood (DAL) moves forward into Green's (GSW) body and initiates contact that affects his layup attempt.
Kumimga (GSW) briefly places a forearm on Doncic (DAL) on the perimeter and the contact is marginal.
DiVincenzo (GSW) jumps vertically and absorbs the ensuing contact that occurs during Wood's (DAL) layup attempt.

Bullock (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Curry (GSW) on the perimeter.  He briefly places an arm around Curry, but the contact is marginal and Curry loses his balance on his own.
Replay review of the OOB called on Curry (GSW) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Curry is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.
Kuminga (GSW) is in a legal guarding position while defending Doncic (DAL) as he dribbles up the floor.  He then briefly places a hand on his hip and immediately removes it.
Doncic (DAL) switches his pivot foot prior to the jump shot attempt.
Green (GSW) reaches for the loose ball and grazes Doncic's (DAL) front.  The contact is marginal and does not impact Doncic's ability to pursue the rebound.
Green (GSW) and Doncic (DAL) reach for the rebound and possession is awarded to GSW. There is no clear and conclusive angle that shows the call was incorrect.
Green (GSW) turns towards Bullock (DAL) during the defensive switch and the contact is marginal.
Kleber (DAL) is in a legal guarding position while defending Curry (GSW) on the perimeter.  He briefly places a hand to his front and the contact is marginal.
Green (GSW) backs into Bullock (DAL) in the lane but does not hold him or otherwise dislodge him from his defensive position.
Green (GSW) is in a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact with Doncic (DAL) during his layup attempt.
Green (DAL) commits a take foul on Looney (GSW).
Thompson (GSW) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Bullock's (DAL) arm.
